# Secrets — never commit real tokens
# Info.plist contains the OpenClawToken placeholder; if you fill in the real token
# directly there, add it to git's exclude list or use the OPENCLAW_TOKEN env var.
# Secrets.xcconfig (if you create one with the real token) must be gitignored:
Secrets.xcconfig
